Takealot has opened pre-orders for the Apple iPhone 11, 11 Pro, and 11 Pro Max. The new iPhone is available in a range of colours and storage sizes from Takealot, starting with the iPhone 11 64GB and going up to the iPhone 11 Pro Max 512GB. Click here to order your new iPhone 11 from Takealot Pre-orders of the device will start shipping on 27 September 2019. Takealot is also running a special for the first 50 shoppers who complete their iPhone 11 pre-order. The first 50 shoppers with confirmed payment for their iPhone 11 pre-order will receive a R1,000 Takealot voucher, for use on their next order. Terms and conditions do apply.  